title: Silver Legion Militia Unbanned
subtitle: The judges have re-legalized the Silver Legion militia.
view-if: sa_banned == 1 and sa_ban_timer == 0 and judicial_reform < 2
on-arrival: sa_banned = 0; sa_strength += 100; sa_militancy += 0.04
tags: event

Judges have ordered the Silver Legion militia to be re-legalized. They immediately return to mass recruiting and arming.
